# Day 1296

Cleaning up my space is elite. Not fun to do, but I always feel better after. Exercising is another one of those things.

![You can raise your energy by doing the things you just intrinsically know you should do](https://miro.medium.com/1*7FxLQskEh8Fttsn9TapB3w.png)

It is all turtles, all the way down.

A strange loop, if you will/

10/8/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
